Usage guide for managing data.js through data_manager.js tool: 

Added mass data.js management tool
Created data_manager.js.

You can use it for:



bash
node data_manager.js ./data.js summary
node data_manager.js ./data.js verify [limit]
node data_manager.js ./data.js audit-feet defenders 50
node data_manager.js ./data.js audit-feet all 50
node data_manager.js ./data.js audit-tier 20
node data_manager.js ./data.js audit-consistency 20
node data_manager.js ./data.js fix-consistency
node data_manager.js ./data.js export-csv data_export.csv
node data_manager.js ./data.js patch-csv edits.csv
node data_manager.js ./data.js cap-feet defenders
node data_manager.js ./data.js cap-feet all
node data_manager.js ./data.js scale CB rightFoot 0.85
node data_manager.js ./data.js set "Simon Francis" rightFoot 76 --all
node data_manager.js ./data.js set-tier "Player Name" L --all
node data_manager.js ./data.js backup



Added overall recalculation script
Created recalculate_overall.js.

Usage:




bash
node recalculate_overall.js ./data.js write
Check-only mode:




bash
node recalculate_overall.js ./data.js check 25
It recalculates overall based on current attributes and position-specific formulas.

